snippet.title: The Right Take
snippet.description:
Hey guys!
Welcome to The Right Take!!
We are a channel that focuses on whatever is hot and drama filled in the world of social media and celebrities!!
If you like these types of videos make sure to subscribe and check out our weekly videos !!

We are always right... just remember that ;)
